                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18401019-name-490" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-490" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-490" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-490" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS LEWIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a tallow-chandler's, shop in Whitechapel. On the 25th of September, about twelve o'clock in the morning, I was at the back of my house, and saw the prisoner coming from behind my counter—I came in and said, "You villain, what do you do here?"—I let him go, but my wife came in, and missed three half-crowns from the till.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
