                  </hi>. I sell oysters in the street. On the 25th of Sep<lb></lb>tember the prisoner came to me and had 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. worth of oysters—he went to a shop and changed one half-crown, and I saw two others in his hand—I do not know what time it was.</p>
